snippet.title: Zombies.io  Fun New Zombie game by SideQuest Development!
snippet.description:
Whats going on everyone, this is a new zombie game by SideQuest Development.  This game is a lot of fun, there wasn't really a lot of players on this time, but stay tuned for more videos, I will get one where the server has more people.  You can play the game for free by clicking on the link below.

www.zombies.io

This is the SideQuest Discord:  https://discord.gg/sidequest

A Special Thanks to Andy from SideQuest for being an Awesome Dev.
